<p>
For some of the more tricky ceramics, one must apply a special glaze to finish it off. And the proper bowl to create them in is the glaze mortar. These are all no-fail combines... just mix in the correct ingredients. But don't blame us if you don't apply the glaze to the correct unfired item.
</p><br><div align="right">Last Modified By: EQTC Editor Krazick&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>

